depositCollateral(address,address).details: The collateral might be returned if the validator is not registered in the consensus layer.

params.collateralOwner: The address to own the collateral.

registerValidator(address,bytes,address).details: The collateral might be returned if the validator is not registered in the consensus layer.

params.initialCollateralOwner: The initial address to own the initial collateral.
params.pubKey: The compressed 33-byte secp256k1 public key of the validator.

transferCollateralOwnership(address,addr.details: Nothing happens if the validator is not registered in the consensus layer.

params.newOwner: The address to receive the ownership of the collateral.
params.prevOwner: The address that owns the collateral.

unjail(address).details: Nothing happens if the validator is not jailed in the consensus layer.

updateExtraVotingPower(address,uint256).details: Nothing happens if the validator is not registered in the consensus layer.

params.extraVotingPower: The new extra voting power of the validator.

withdrawCollateral(address,address,addre.details: Nothing happens if the validator is not registered in the consensus layer or the collateral owner don't own enough collateral.

params.amount: The amount of collateral to withdraw.
params.collateralOwner: The address that owns the collateral.
params.maturesAt: The time when the withdrawal request matures. After this time, the collateral will be sent to the receiver.
params.receiver: The address to receive the withdrawn collateral.

depositCollateral(address,address).notice: Deposit collateral to the validator in the consensus layer.

registerValidator(address,bytes,address).notice: Register a validator in the consensus layer.

transferCollateralOwnership(address,addr.notice: Transfer the ownership of the collateral to a new address.

unjail(address).notice: Unjail a validator in the consensus layer.

updateExtraVotingPower(address,uint256).notice: Update (overwrite) the extra voting power of a validator in the consensus layer.

withdrawCollateral(address,address,addre.notice: Request a withdrawal of collateral from the validator in the consensus layer. The collateral is sent to the receiver address after the request matures.
